{"tid":1254280,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「 拆彈」中國外交部狂言 G20峰會期間不容許討論香港問題","createTime":"2019-06-24T04:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T04:56:59.000Z","uid":265168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad5c82654ca7dc774263c6d0fef1b02850f032b","tid":1254280,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T04:56:59.000Z","msg":"20大工業國高峰會（G20）即將在本周末於日本大阪舉行，外界預料外國領袖很可能會趁此向中國關切香港反送中大規模示威。對此，中國外交部官員今日態度強硬表示，不可能允許他人在G20上討論香港問題，並重申不允許任何國家干涉中國內政。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25VaC66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25VaC66.jpg&h=2c4883e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wbrk0ks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbrk0ks.jpg&h=5649bfb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6.26 6.27 香港人加油！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZHZe4Ou.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZHZe4Ou.jpg&h=34401e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3BEiM1M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3BEiM1M.jpg&h=3c1716b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pDaFfU7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpDaFfU7.jpg&h=24db2501&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}